    "Radius-adj shows the adjusted values in the 2010s by using the following equation.",
    "Regarding the patent, the mean adjusted radius to the 200th neighbor document increases from 0.1793 to 0.1911, representing an increase of 6.5%.",
    "In the case of the original value (0.1918 in the 2010s), it increases by 7.0%.",
    "In contrast, the same measure is relatively stable for research papers (0.1645 to 0.1661, 1.0% growth).",
    "These findings imply that the technological frontier measured by patent expands to more sparse places in the technology space."
